<item>
            <title>[CODEC-221] HmacUtils.updateHmac calls reset() unnecessarily</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CODEC-221</link>
                <project id="12310464" key="CODEC">Commons Codec</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The HmacUtils.updateHmac() methods call reset().&lt;br/&gt;
This means that it&apos;s not possible to build up a digest using multiple such calls.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The only useful operation that can be performed afterwards is to call one of the Mac.doFinal() methods.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately it&apos;s probably too late to change this.&lt;br/&gt;
However it should at least be documented.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
